[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53210/?][/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49676/?]Skyrim Realistic Texture Overhaul Mountains[/url][/center]


Skyrim Realistic Texture Overhaul Farmhouses Gives you lore friendly sharp textures with parallax effects and bug fixes. Well made Normal maps and parallax maps gives this mod a great deal of depth.

[center]SRTO Farmhouses offers you:
~It covers parallax for nearly all textures in farmhouse category (if needed).
~HD/HQ uncompressed normal maps.
~HD/HQ uncompressed Parallax maps.
~Ambient occlusion (AO) is also included in the textures.
~Disabled specular for thatch roofs as they don't reflect in real life unless raining.
~More to come.[/center]

[center][youtube]PuBjdIICovw[/youtube][/center]


Install:
First of all: Download [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/8655/?]Static Mesh Improvement Mod - SMIM by Brumbek[/url]
Second: Download one of my main files with SMIM patch in optional files
Use NMM or drop the data folder in your Skyrim folder

[color=#FF0000] *ATTENTION* DO NOT USE ANY SOFTWARE TO OPTIMIZE YOUR TEXTURES, IT WILL RUIN MY TEXTURES, MY MOD IS OPTIMIZED FROM RELEASE *ATTENTION*Â [/color]
author: Frozunswaidon

files.name: Skyrim Realistic Texture Overhaul Farms 2K
files.changelogHtml:
SMIM patch COMPLETE 100%. Enjoy Parallax with SMIM features, interiors and exteriors!

New interior floor texture! Weathered the thatch and applied a better alpha. Remade the walkway planks with a better normal and improved the parallax map some.
